{"tid":1171150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國予黃台仰李東昇難民庇護　中國外交部駐港公署召德領事提嚴正交涉","createTime":"2019-05-25T13:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T14:36:50.000Z","uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f2759d47f6c5661236fb88368a823e2fd120f844","tid":1171150,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:31:21.000Z","msg":"參與旺角大衝突、涉嫌干犯暴動罪棄保潛逃的本土民主前線黃台仰和李東昇，去年獲德國批出難民庇護申請。中國外交部駐港特派員公署今日（25日）在網頁公布，公署負責人昨緊急約見德國駐香港代理總領事施密特，就事件向德方提出嚴正交涉，表達「強烈不滿和堅決反對」。<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港公署敦促德國恪守國際法和國際關係基本準則，切實尊重香港的法治和司法獨立，「認清錯誤，改弦易轍，不得縱容和包庇犯罪分子，不得干預香港事務和中國內政」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190525/s00001/1558788034539/德國予黃台仰李東昇難民庇護-外交部駐港公署召德領事提嚴正交涉\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190525%2Fs00001%2F1558788034539%2F%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%88%E9%BB%83%E5%8F%B0%E4%BB%B0%E6%9D%8E%E6%9D%B1%E6%98%87%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7-%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2%E5%8F%AC%E5%BE%B7%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B%E6%8F%90%E5%9A%B4%E6%AD%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%B6%89&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFIVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=96569e0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190525%2Fs00001%2F1558788034539%2F%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%88%E9%BB%83%E5%8F%B0%E4%BB%B0%E6%9D%8E%E6%9D%B1%E6%98%87%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7-%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2%E5%8F%AC%E5%BE%B7%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B%E6%8F%90%E5%9A%B4%E6%AD%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%B6%89&h=596b1f37\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190525/s00001/1558788034539/德國予黃台仰李東昇難民庇護-外交部駐港公署召德領事提嚴正交涉</a>"},{"pid":"7867c32ab5c8f68a0ca4002c9a4452c8471a49a0","tid":1171150,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:03:05.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"5e496ac6c37c24a5f6ed3c4e06e734e156858642","tid":1171150,"uid":